Lego Universe is an upcoming [[massively multiplayer online game]] being developed by [[NetDevil]]. It is planned to be released in the Autumn of 2010. Its release has been delayed from original estimates of 2009,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5056497/lego-universe-already-in-some-gamers-hands |title=A Visit to NetDevil |publisher=Kotaku.com |date=2008-09-29 |accessdate=2010-01-16}}</ref> late November 2008,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lego.com/eng/info/default.asp?page=productsdetail&contentid=36621 |title=The Lego Group announces Lego Universe as official title for branded MMOG |publisher=Lego.com |date=2007-06-07 |accessdate=2010-01-16}}</ref> and mid-2008.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://loot-ninja.com/2007/06/01/lego-mmo-screens-and-info/ |title=Lego MMO Screens and Info |publisher=Loot-ninja.com |date=2007-06-01 |accessdate=2010-01-16}}</ref> This will be the first Lego [[computer game]] sold in which players can connect and play [[online]], and will be only available in [[English language|English]].<ref>[http://shop.lego.com/Product/?p=2855133 Lego Shop for Lego Universe Pre-Order]</ref> The game is currently in the [[Lego universe#Beta|Closed Beta]] stage of testing.
